[2026-05-28 14:49:50.88467] [2812007] [debug] 	<pre>
[2026-05-28 14:49:50.88469] [2812007] [debug] 	Code to test something hashy
[2026-05-28 14:49:50.88470] [2812007] [debug] 	perl -MHash::Util=lock_keys -e '%hash = map {; $_ => $_ } (0 .. 1_000); lock_keys(%hash); for (1 .. 1_000_000) { my $x = $hash{ int(rand() * 1_000) } }'
