[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97769] [2812007] [info] Topic: id: 176. html_id: 1760000. title: TiddlyWikis
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97775] [2812007] [debug] 	o See also
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97777] [2812007] [debug] 	- WikiStuff
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97778] [2812007] [debug] 	- https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax - Syntax reference
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97780] [2812007] [debug] 	- https://feather.wiki/ - For Feather Wiki, a tiny version of a TiddlyWiki
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97781] [2812007] [debug] 	- https://foswiki.org/Home/About - For FosWiki, a collaboration tool
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97783] [2812007] [debug] 	- https://tiddlywiki.com/ - The TiddlyWiki ecosystem
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97784] [2812007] [debug] 	<pre>
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97787] [2812007] [debug] Unknown: Care! TiddlyWikis contains executable code in order to provide all the features listed below
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97789] [2812007] [error] Token: Care! TiddlyWikis contains executable code in order to provide all the features listed below. Missing lines
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97794] [2812007] [debug] Unknown: Overview
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97796] [2812007] [debug] Token: Overview. Extras:
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97798] [2812007] [debug] 	- The purpose of these restrictions is to impose guidelines for the naming of things
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97800] [2812007] [debug] 	- These guidelines help people with no expertise in data collation to index items carefully
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97801] [2812007] [debug] 	- So, they help prevent growth-like-topsy, a major problem will old-style wikis
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97803] [2812007] [debug] 	- Do yourself a favour and always include a para in every TiddlyWiki called MainMenu (or Index or TableOfContents), and put in it an alphabetical list of para names
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97981] [2812007] [debug] Unknown: Inbuilt features of all TiddlyWikis
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97984] [2812007] [debug] Token: Inbuilt features of all TiddlyWikis. Extras:
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97986] [2812007] [debug] 	- The 3 double-quotes at the top of this para is one such command, but they are only visible when you click the pencil (edit) icon to enter edit mode for a para
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97988] [2812007] [debug] 	- Encryption (good for passwords)
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97989] [2812007] [debug] 	- History of paras edited per day
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97991] [2812007] [debug] 	- Import capability (a way of sharing)
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.97992] [2812007] [debug] 	- Programmable in that you can list what paras are to be opened automatically when the file is loaded into the web client (browser). Hence the para called GettingStarted
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98141] [2812007] [debug] Unknown: On-line help
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98144] [2812007] [debug] Token: On-line help. Extras:
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98146] [2812007] [debug] 	- It is quite different than my GettingStarted para
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98148] [2812007] [debug] 	- In the eco-system there are various public hosting options giving other ways to share besides the import feature mentioned above
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98149] [2812007] [debug] 	</pre>
[2026-05-28 14:49:55.98329] [2812007] [info] --------------------------------------------------
